    "en": {
      "title": "Cockroaches in Pakistan Parliament's food",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The authorities have taken steps to seal two dining halls of the Pakistani Parliament. That was after receiving complaints from the ministers that there were cockroaches in the food taken from the canteens.",
        "According to Pakistani media reports, after receiving the complaints, Islamabad public health inspectors suddenly broke into the Parliament complex and inspected the canteens, after which they decided to seal the canteens.",
        "After the raid, the public health inspectors told the media that both the sealed canteens were in very dirty conditions."
      ],
